<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy">
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-medium text-gray-900 mb-6">Privacy Policy</h1>

    <div class="space-y-6 text-gray-800 leading-relaxed">
      <p>
        Your privacy is important to <strong>The Life Place</strong>. This policy explains what information we collect,
        how we use it, and your choices.
      </p>

      <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-medium">Information We Collect</h3>
      <p>
        We may collect basic contact details you voluntarily provide (e.g., forms), and anonymous analytics (if enabled).
      </p>

      <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-medium">How We Use Information</h3>
      <p>
        To respond to enquiries, improve our website, and communicate church updates (only with your consent).
      </p>

      <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-medium">Data Sharing</h3>
      <p>
        We donâ€™t sell your data. We only share with service providers who help us run this site, under proper safeguards.
      </p>

      <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-medium">Your Choices</h3>
      <p>
        You can request access or deletion of your personal info by emailing
        <a href="mailto:hello@thelifeplace.org" class="text-[#B3282D] underline hover:underline">hello@thelifeplace.org</a>
      </p>

      <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-medium">Updates</h3>
      <p>
        We may update this policy from time to time. Please check this page periodically for changes.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>